## Liferay Support TSE Internal Training - Git ##
* author: david zhang
* date:   2017-3-5
* version: 1.0

### Purpose ###
this artcile is to help our new TSE to have a whole idea how liferay uses git to manage the code. it will start from git basis to advance.




######Prepration
* How To Install Git
  https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Getting-Started-Installing-Git

* How to fork Liferay-Portal resource.
  https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal

#####  Basis
* where to clone/download the source ?
  git clone https://github.com/daviddotzhang/liferay-portal.git
* Update to latest is a necessary before doing any thing.
  git pull --rebase upstream master
  

